# Large run artifacts — never committed (spec rule 9). Small analysis-summary
# JSONs under experiments/{calibrations,analysis_m5,comparisons} and
# reports/figures ARE committed so notebooks/site rebuild without retraining
# (spec rule 14: analysis must not require re-training).
checkpoints/
experiments/runs/
reports/env/
reports/html/assets/
# Vendored Plotly runtime (3.5MB) — regenerated by build scripts / `make site`
reports/site/assets/

# Downloaded corpus texts / snapshots / tokenized caches / SFT data
# (manifests ARE committed; the data is rebuildable from them)
data/samples/*.txt
data/snapshots/
data/tokenized/
data/sft/

# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.ipynb_checkpoints/
.pytest_cache/
